                    <h3 class="font-minecraft text-xl mb-4">Discord Bot 2GB</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6">
                        <li>10GB NVMe SSD</li>
                        <li>Unmetered Bandwidth</li>
                        <li>MySQL & PostgreSQL</li>
                        <li>Global Locations</li>
